44:09.610 --> 44:11.779
Hit up the ravine, shoot bottles.

44:12.655 --> 44:14.532
So, they were practicing?

44:15.199 --> 44:16.909
Where'd they get the money?

44:17.326 --> 44:19.829
I don't care as long
as their money's good.

44:20.454 --> 44:21.455
Got another beer?

44:40.349 --> 44:41.643
Mr. Mason?

44:55.906 --> 44:56.866
Hi.

44:57.826 --> 44:58.785
Hello.

45:00.954 --> 45:01.955
I...

45:02.956 --> 45:05.457
I got your address
from the registrar's office.

45:05.457 --> 45:08.753
- Is Teddy okay?
- Yes, he's fine.

45:10.255 --> 45:13.049
I was worried
they were gonna kick him out.

45:14.216 --> 45:16.970
Well, I smoothed things over
with the school.

45:18.263 --> 45:19.598
What did you say?

45:20.140 --> 45:23.726
I told them the truth.
The other father started it.

45:31.610 --> 45:32.819
Well...

45:35.154 --> 45:37.573
I stopped and got you something. It's...

45:37.991 --> 45:40.619
French Dip from Cole's.
